<refsection condition='ref.description'>
<title>Description</title>


<para>A <tag>Synopsis</tag> is a verbatim environment for displaying command,
function, and other syntax summaries.
</para>

<para>Unlike <tag>CmdSynopsis</tag> and <tag>FuncSynopsis</tag> which have a
complex interior structure,
<tag>Synopsis</tag> is simply a verbatim environment.
</para>

<refsection><title>Processing expectations</title>
<para><?tdg gentext='pexp.linespecific'?> <tag>Synopsis</tag> elements are usually
displayed in a fixed width font.
</para>
</refsection> 

